Recorded (5L JMA) in Fukushima; (4 JMA) in Iwate, Miyagi and Tochigi; (3 JMA) in Akita, Aomori, Chiba, Gumma, Ibaraki, Kanagawa, Niigata, Saitama, Tokyo, Yamagata and Yamanashi; (2 JMA) in Nagano and Shizuoka; (1 JMA) in Aichi, Gifu, Ishikawa and Shiga. Also recorded (2 JMA) in southern and southwestern Hokkaido and (1 JMA) in central and eastern Hokkaido. Recorded (1 JMA) on Hachijo-jima, Miyake-jima, O-shima and Sadoga-shima.
